Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants that include Completed + In Call versus variants that do not
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Resolved in cases where Completed + In Call appears earlier in the trace
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait to Completed + Closed in traces containing Completed + In Call versus those without
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait grouped by country to assess regional differences in waiting behavior
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time between Accepted + In Progress and Accepted + Wait when Completed + In Call is present later in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait in high-frequency variants (e.g., top 5 most frequent) that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait in variants where Completed + In Call occurs before it versus after it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait in traces that transition directly to Completed + Resolved after Accepted + Wait, compared to those that go through Completed + In Call first
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait in variants starting with Queued + Awaiting Assignment and containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Time from case start until Accepted + Wait is performed in cases that eventually execute Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + In Call when they appear consecutively or with only one intermediate activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait in variants where it is immediately followed by Accepted + In Progress and later includes Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'
